{
  "stem": "18670.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 349.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I got a job in a clothing factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I started working.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "19.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Wait a minute. 1940, I was 21 already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My brother didn't get a job right away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Grandpa used to have a pot and a gas flame cooking with the bare blocks in it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I know there's a Jewish method with little pieces of meat and it would boil all day long.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I came home in the evening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said to him my brother was hungry, was a growing boy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said-- and he said he only got-- fed him once during the day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I asked how come.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said to me [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the answer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was my other experience with religion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you-- were you accepted by the rest of the family in--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was accepted by one aunt who came originally from Czechoslovakia, the mother of the cousin that was involved in getting us here.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The rest of the family, the other uncles, felt-- I found out later on they felt that they were involved in-- that we might take the money that Grandfather has.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As [INAUDIBLE] in the end, the money was in the safe of his president of his shul.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when Grandpa died, he had got the money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I know it was about $8,000 he had in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there' was another involvement.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One of the uncles, the youngest one, Jack, who-- my brother finally got a job, delivery boy for a butcher shop on 172nd Street, who happened to be a German refugee who had a butcher shop there.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My brother would deliver, get some money in tips.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he got paid $12 a week.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
